{
  "stem": "7546.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we lived next door to each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- and I was all alone, so they were sort of the-- the-- the tower of my strength, having two sisters and two brother-in-laws.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I felt, every time they looked at me, I-- I see that love is transposing on me because her daughter, her eight-year-old daughter, was with my parents.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And maybe they're still alive, although they were dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] We didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't believe that there is such thing as burning people, killing people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shooting people, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But organized burning, organized gassing, or just organized killing, organized murder-- that something like this could exist in a country such as Germany, I didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I honestly didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I read some-- some of the books.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I read some of the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I heard about the book that Hitler wrote when he was in jail in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In 1923, he was in jail when he wrote I-- I heard some excerpts from his book.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he only said that he will destroy the Jewish race as a nation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He never talked about burning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The only time I heard about burning Jews was in the 7th century, when Martin Luther, in Germany, read a book- wrote the book about destroying the infidels.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the 17th-- what  did I say, 19th?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, in the 17th century, Martin Luther advocated total and complete destruction of Jewish nation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of these excerpts found themselves in which Hitler used.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was also something unbelievable, even if I were to go back to the 15th century, of the Inquisition.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was a choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you wanted to become a Christian, you became a Marrano, and you lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
